{"tid":262444,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[IKEA點讀]日本仔唔識點讀ASUS","createTime":"2017-05-29T08:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T09:40:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b38bde5db2a718d1050687ee2b54261170e405f0","tid":262444,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"COSTCO、IKEA這兩大商場的名字唸法經常成為台灣鄉民的惡搞梗，不過昨天讓日本網友碰上同樣煩惱的卻是台灣電腦廠商ASUS（華碩）！許多網友都以為唸成ASUS或ASUS，事實上ASUS官方早就在2012年確定標準唸法是ASUS，以後大家不要再念錯啦！原來日本也會玩這個梗啊&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>ASUS衝上日本推特熱門話題榜</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dbSaoge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdbSaoge.jpg&h=32a0f346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左ASUS唔識讀之外仲有NVIDIA、imgur同OIOI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NCTRWQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNCTRWQG.jpg&h=1b571958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩埋投票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dRHHTNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdRHHTNI.jpg&h=a51adce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連官方自己都玩埋一份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6PLQRAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6PLQRAi.jpg&h=fe4f7a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1498629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1498629&d=ZhvbC5Rzy8qi6gYmOdFFaJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=054c46d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1498629</a>"},{"pid":"8a92b07077a4982a4baad1206ff1c6844c6839c2","tid":262444,"uid":70916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"好撚過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c7fa278278e509819096a72cc83c0b40eba33","tid"